title: Top Places to visit in Naidupet, Andhra Pradesh
content:
Naidupeta is a Town & Municipality in the Nellore district of the Indian state of Andhra Pradesh. It also the divisional headquarters and Mandal headquarters of Naidupeta revenue division.

 

Transport

 

Naidupeta Railway station

The Andhra Pradesh State Road Transport Corporation operates bus services from Naidupeta bus station.

 

Naidupeta has a railway station on Chennai - Hyderabad route operated by South Central Railways.

 

source: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naidupeta
